This is a list of the main career statistics of English professional [[darts]] player, '''[[Phil Taylor (darts player)|Phil Taylor]]'''. After his retirement after the 2018 PDC World Championship Taylor has won '''214''' Titles and has been [[Runner-up]] in '''46''' finals. He has also been a Runner-up in '''2 team event''' finals. He has won a record 85 major titles and he has won a record 16 [[World Professional Darts Championship|World Championships]].
